item.title: Sports Have Never Been Better… or More Precarious
item.description:
The PosCast is back with recurring guest Michael Schur! Mike goes on a rant about the state of sports, then the guys are joined by baseball writer Molly Knight to dig even deeper into the inevitable demise of sports as we know it.
